snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' Vs. Ankha !
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' vs. Ankha !
Come play this new FNF Mod, starring the popular Animal Crossing character, Ankha !
As of now there's only one extra song, but there will be more !
Next update will have K.K. Bazaar, and K.K. Bubblegum ! 

Download Links :
Gamebanana : https://gamebanana.com/mods/322139
GameJolt : https://gamejolt.com/games/vsankha/648326 
Source Code : https://github.com/akirawav3/vsAnkha

Song by itself uploaded later, thanks for watching !
